com.exacttarget.etpushsdk
Class ETData

java.lang.Object
  com.exacttarget.etpushsdk.ETData

public class ETData
extends java.lang.Object

Primary data object. Holds all of the data to be sent to or from ExactTarget regarding push or the user.

uniqueDeviceIdentifier

public java.lang.String uniqueDeviceIdentifier(android.content.Context c)
Retrieves a unique, non-identifiable, non-changing device identifier. Note that this is not the same as the GCM token - this can be used in it's absence, and will be used to uniquely identify devices to ExactTarget.

Parameters:
c - Context of the application
Returns:
Device identifier
